{
    "body": "<p>The following feats are unique to kobolds.</p>", 
    "name": "Kobold Feats", 
    "url": "pfsrd://Monster Codex/Rules/Kobolds/New Rules/Kobold Feats", 
    "type": "section", 
    "source": "Monster Codex", 
    "sections": [
        {
            "body": "<p>Your draconic aspect manifests as magical might.</p>", 
            "name": "Draconic Magic", 
            "url": "pfsrd://Monster Codex/Rules/Kobolds/New Rules/Kobold Feats/Draconic Magic", 
            "type": "section", 
            "source": "Monster Codex", 
            "sections": [
                {
                    "body": "<p class=\"stat-block-1\">Draconic Aspect, kobold.</p>", 
                    "source": "Monster Codex", 
                    "type": "section", 
                    "name": "Prerequisites"
                }, 
                {
                    "body": "<p class=\"stat-block-1\">You gain a group of spell-like abilities based on the color of your dragon aspect. Each spell-like ability can be used once per day, and the DC of any of these spell-like abilities is 10 + 1/2 your Hit Dice + Charisma modifier.</p>", 
                    "type": "section", 
                    "sections": [
                        {
                            "body": "<p class=\"stat-block-2\"> : <i>Corrosive touch</i> <span class=\"char-style-override-69\">, </span><sup>&dagger;</sup>, <i>darkness</i> .</p>", 
                            "url": "pfsrd://Monster Codex/Rules/Kobolds/New Rules/Kobold Feats/Draconic Magic/Benefit/Black", 
                            "type": "section", 
                            "name": "Black", 
                            "source": "Monster Codex"
                        }, 
                        {
                            "body": "<p class=\"stat-block-2\"> : <i>Minor image</i>, <i>shocking grasp</i> <sup>&dagger;</sup>.</p>", 
                            "url": "pfsrd://Monster Codex/Rules/Kobolds/New Rules/Kobold Feats/Draconic Magic/Benefit/Blue", 
                            "type": "section", 
                            "name": "Blue", 
                            "source": "Monster Codex"
                        }, 
                        {
                            "body": "<p class=\"stat-block-2\"> : <i>Entangle</i> <sup>&dagger;</sup>, <i>gust of wind</i> .</p>", 
                            "url": "pfsrd://Monster Codex/Rules/Kobolds/New Rules/Kobold Feats/Draconic Magic/Benefit/Green", 
                            "type": "section", 
                            "name": "Green", 
                            "source": "Monster Codex"
                        }, 
                        {
                            "body": "<p class=\"stat-block-2\"> : <i>Burning hands</i> <sup>&dagger;</sup>, <i>pyrotechnics</i> .</p>", 
                            "url": "pfsrd://Monster Codex/Rules/Kobolds/New Rules/Kobold Feats/Draconic Magic/Benefit/Red", 
                            "type": "section", 
                            "name": "Red", 
                            "source": "Monster Codex"
                        }, 
                        {
                            "body": "<p class=\"stat-block-2\"> : <i>Burning hands</i> <sup>&dagger;</sup> (deals cold damage instead of fire),<i> fog cloud</i> .</p>", 
                            "url": "pfsrd://Monster Codex/Rules/Kobolds/New Rules/Kobold Feats/Draconic Magic/Benefit/White", 
                            "type": "section", 
                            "name": "White", 
                            "source": "Monster Codex"
                        }
                    ], 
                    "name": "Benefit", 
                    "source": "Monster Codex"
                }, 
                {
                    "body": "<p class=\"stat-block-1\">You can use this feat instead of Draconic Breath or Draconic Glide to qualify for the Draconic Paragon feat. If you have this feat and Draconic Paragon, you can use the spell-like ability marked with a dagger (&dagger;) twice per day.</p>", 
                    "source": "Monster Codex", 
                    "type": "section", 
                    "name": "Special"
                }
            ]
        }, 
        {
            "body": "<p>You are skilled at riding slurks into battle.</p>", 
            "name": "Slurk Rider", 
            "url": "pfsrd://Monster Codex/Rules/Kobolds/New Rules/Kobold Feats/Slurk Rider", 
            "type": "section", 
            "source": "Monster Codex", 
            "abbrev": "Combat", 
            "sections": [
                {
                    "body": "<p class=\"stat-block-1\">Kobold.</p>", 
                    "source": "Monster Codex", 
                    "type": "section", 
                    "name": "Prerequisite"
                }, 
                {
                    "body": "<p class=\"stat-block-1\">You are able to control, guide, and communicate with slurks (<i>Pathfinder RPG Bestiary 2</i> 251), as if they understood Draconic. You can also spend a standard action to manipulate the nodules on the slurk's back to activate its slime ability. Both you and the slurk can activate this ability during the same round.</p>", 
                    "source": "Monster Codex", 
                    "type": "section", 
                    "name": "Benefit"
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}